{"tid":2081983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府墮騙局 物流署購涉違《商品說明》口罩","createTime":"2020-06-27T15:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T16:57:51.000Z","uid":89543,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4df013008eedb04d17d22c32184354a42dcac6","tid":2081983,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/IXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3VtDbNou6k3z1rb6wPyZ7t6Ocq-g6lkbRY03XWZPq8qlI-VwneigP-C0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FIXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3VtDbNou6k3z1rb6wPyZ7t6Ocq-g6lkbRY03XWZPq8qlI-VwneigP-C0c&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=00506341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FIXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3VtDbNou6k3z1rb6wPyZ7t6Ocq-g6lkbRY03XWZPq8qlI-VwneigP-C0c&h=47c89dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/IXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3VtDbNou6k3z1rb6wPyZ7t6Ocq-g6lkbRY03XWZPq8qlI-VwneigP-C0c</a><br />\n<br />\n年初武漢肺炎肆虐，市民四出奔走排隊撲罩，惟政府沿用「價低者得」方式招標，被批反應遲緩、離地。而直到2月尾，政府物流服務署方完成招標採購5,700萬個口罩。但周六（27日）深夜政府公佈，一批3月購入的口罩，部份涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》。有傳媒則報道指，海關已拘捕4人及搜查2間相關公司。<br />\n<br />\n政府周六晚公佈物流署3月購入的口罩中，有部份涉違反《商品說明條例》。物流署指口罩已分發至不同政府部門，現時已通知各政府部門暫停使用該批口罩，並會向其供應商追討損失。物流署亦懷疑該供應商曾提交虛假文件，已報警處理。惟政府聲明未有透露獲分發該批口罩的政府部門、相關口罩數量、涉及金額等資料。<br />\n<br />\n年初口罩荒時，政府被揭一直以「價低者得」的方式招標購買口罩。直至今年2月21日，政府物流服務署接受傳媒查詢時稱，已公開招標採購5,700萬個口罩，並於當日截標，共接獲3份標書。該標書的規格要求指，口罩須獲第三方認可獨立實驗室，認證其BFE、PFE率不少於95%、壓力差不多於4.0mm，及合成血液穿透阻力為80mmHg。<br />\n<br />\n惟物流署當時以口罩採購競爭激烈為由，拒絕公開口罩供應商、口罩購入量、牽涉金額等資料，指會損害政府議價能力。直至4月物流署回覆立法會議員時指，有超過2,000萬個相關口罩已送達，惟供應商等資料依然未明。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局曾於2月，向政府各部門發通告，透露政府物流署購入的口罩只會分發予醫護、從事隔離措施人員、政治清潔工及院舍職員等，而各部門則可以自行採購口罩，只要定單為1,000萬以下，就能毋須政策局批准直接採購，未知今次涉事口罩是否已分發予相關部門。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在月初口罩短缺問題最嚴重時，表示感謝中央支持特區政府，指醫管局、特區政府和批發商，成功購入1,700萬個內地批發商供應的口罩。其後物流署便在未有公佈供應商資料的情況下，批出5,700萬個口罩的合約。"},{"pid":"66c828b245f96b510173806ad6a0c993c414c782","tid":2081983,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0bd58b9cbf1eeb96b4146f7984cd62dc6c0f87","tid":2081983,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"咪又係益藍屍老千"},{"pid":"98c6a726e670b14f137f50093c98adc0bb094dc6","tid":2081983,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312145cde32855592a93f1a4cdf322fb724c693a","tid":2081983,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多「誤墮」騙局啊 中間有冇人袋咗錢啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29e11edfd903e0e6fa86e38215c49240a8b38f2","tid":2081983,"uid":32150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2142d22a640fe113f7c320a6955a24489bea608","tid":2081983,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:44:48.000Z","msg":"所以免費派返比市民，都估到政府邊有咁好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7792d74f3121bc47887f047952887b4770c16a","tid":2081983,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2142d22a640fe113f7